gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Rockets 114, Suns 110
gameRecap.excerpt: The Rockets defeated the Suns, 114-110. Fred VanVleet led the way with 23 points, five rebounds, and five assists for the Rockets, with Jabari Smith Jr. adding 22 points and 16 rebounds in the victory. Bol Bol tallied a season-high 25 points and 14 rebounds for the Suns in the defeat. The Rockets improve to 25-31, while the Suns fall to 33-24.
